    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a desolate world as you uncover the fate of those who came before. Solve puzzles, interact with a decaying yet beautiful landscape, and rely on your companion to endure a journey of loss, hope, and discovery. In this atmospheric 2.5D adventure, the world remembers—even if no one else does.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lost, But Never Alone</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/353abe19d51d538f8b36e6cab02366bf.poster.avif?t=1756640464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/353abe19d51d538f8b36e6cab02366bf.webm?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/353abe19d51d538f8b36e6cab02366bf.mp4?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The world is empty, but you are not alone. A steadfast companion walks beside you, a quiet reminder that hope still lingers. In a place where everything has crumbled, only together can you find the strength to move forward.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The world may be fractured, but its mechanisms still hold purpose.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/8b27fcffeca265c8591b21ae75b6c71d.poster.avif?t=1756640464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/8b27fcffeca265c8591b21ae75b6c71d.webm?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/8b27fcffeca265c8591b21ae75b6c71d.mp4?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pathways have crumbled. <br><br>Abandoned machines whisper forgotten functions, leaving behind challenges no one was meant to face, but the answers lie in the world itself—if you know where to look.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MORE THAN A SETTING, A PRESENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/d11d59c495fd21c6e0914ac412e7755b.poster.avif?t=1756640464\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/d11d59c495fd21c6e0914ac412e7755b.webm?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/d11d59c495fd21c6e0914ac412e7755b.mp4?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You were built to navigate, adapt and process data. Yet, as you step into the landscape, your systems flag something untraceable through the logs. The air is heavy, the silence intrusive. This is not just a place—it is a memory. And it lingers within you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A WORLD THAT SPEAKS WITHOUT WORDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/92986920be23df5424e9ffdc130f82f1.poster.avif?t=1756640464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/92986920be23df5424e9ffdc130f82f1.webm?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310850/extras/92986920be23df5424e9ffdc130f82f1.mp4?t=1756640464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ruins hold echoes of the past, their story told in silent remnants and shifting shadows. Every flickering light, every faint transmission—each a sign of what led to this emptiness. Will you piece it together?</p>",
